'''Lily Nyamwasa''' is an actress from [[Wikipedia:Rwanda|Rwanda]] who played [[Jedi Master]] [[Stass Allie]] in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']] and [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']]. Living in [[Wikipedia:Australia|Australia]], Nyamwasa was initially cast to replace [[Gin Clarke]] in the role of [[Jedi|Jedi Master]] [[Adi Gallia]], but the character of Stass Allie was made to accommodate the casting change. Having fled from the [[Wikipedia:Rwandan genocide|Rwandan genocide]], Nyamwasa had signed autographs to raise funds for her charity, Rwandan Orphan Assistance Response.

